metadata.description: Galactus. Thanos. M.O.D.O.K. With her unique combination of wit, empathy, and totally kick-butt squirrel powers, Doreen Green- aka The Unbeatable Squirrel Girl- has taken all these chumps down! Alongside her friends Tippy-Toe (a squirrel) and Nancy (a regular human with no powers whatsoever- they checked), Squirrel Girl is all that stands between the Earth and total destruction!
metadata.name: The Unbeatable Squirrel Girl
